tent\/uploads\/freshizer\/41686effb57d2bedb4aad66d55c7c8fd_86d6eeb10ee6aad9a0bb0dc4777dfa1b_top100-hotels-resorts-world-2022-1920-1080-c-90-768-c-100.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/41686effb57d2bedb4aad66d55c7c8fd_86d6eeb10ee6aad9a0bb0dc4777dfa1b_top100-hotels-resorts-world-2022-1920-1080-c-90-992-c-100.jpg 992w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/41686effb57d2bedb4aad66d55c7c8fd_86d6eeb10ee6aad9a0bb0dc4777dfa1b_top100-hotels-resorts-world-2022-1920-1080-c-90-1200-c-100.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/86d6eeb10ee6aad9a0bb0dc4777dfa1b_top100-hotels-resorts-world-2022-1920-1080-c-90.jpg\" alt=\"top100-hotels-resorts-world-2022\" id=\"Image mobile\"><style><\/style><script type=\"text\/javascript\"><\/script><section class=\"ffb-id-480aar95 fg-section fg-text-dark\" id=\"intro\"><div class=\"fg-container container fg-container-large fg-container-lvl--1 \"><div class=\"fg-row row    \" ><div class=\"ffb-id-480aar96 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><h1 class=\"ffb-id-480aar99 fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\">TOP 100 HOTELS &amp; RESORTS OF THE WORLD 2022<\/h1><div class=\"ffb-id-480aar9a fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Caravelle Saigon is honored to receive two prestige awards from World Luxury Lifestyle Award 2022. These awards represent elite managers and companies with impeccable reputations and professional performances.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Caravelle Family cannot express how happy we are about this. With such great motivation, we will continue bringing the best experiences to our guests in 2023.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">The Organizing Committee evaluated Caravelle Saigon based on voting criteria, including its reputation, luxury service that satisfies the individual needs of guests, prestige, and brand awareness.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Based on this evaluation, we were honored to be awarded TOP 100 Hotels &amp; Resorts of the World 2022.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Amidst our joy, Caravelle Saigon cannot forget that these rewards are all thanks to our valued guests, who remind us to continue bettering ourselves even more!<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">In addition to the Hotel's award, we are proud to share that our General Manager, Mr. Jean Philippe Lovotti, has been awarded the TOP 100 Best General Manager in the World 2022. This prestigious award is given to the best of the best General Manager in the Hospitality industry.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">We appreciate all of your support in achieving these accolades and look forward to welcoming and creating, yet again, more memorable experiences...<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style>.ffb-id-480aar95{ padding-top: 50px;padding-right: 50px;padding-bottom: 50px;padding-left: 50px;}.ffb-id-480aar9a ,.ffb-id-480aar9a:before,.ffb-id-480aar9a:after,.ffb-id-480aar9a *,.ffb-id-480aar9a *:before,.ffb-id-480aar9a *:after{ color: #490042 !important;}.ffb-id-480aar9a{ font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;}.ffb-id-480aar9a:before,.ffb-id-480aar9a:after,.ffb-id-480aar9a:hover,.ffb-id-480aar9a:focus,.ffb-id-480aar9a *,.ffb-id-480aar9a *:before,.ffb-id-480aar9a *:after,.ffb-id-480aar9a *:hover,.ffb-id-480aar9a *:focus{ font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;}.ffb-id-480aar9a{ font-size: 13px !important;}.ffb-id-480aar9a ,.ffb-id-480aar9a:before,.ffb-id-480aar9a:after,.ffb-id-480aar9a:hover,.ffb-id-480aar9a:focus,.ffb-id-480aar9a *,.ffb-id-480aar9a *:before,.ffb-id-480aar9a *:after,.ffb-id-480aar9a *:hover,.ffb-id-480aar9a *:focus{ font-size: 13px !important;}.ffb-id-480aar99 ,.ffb-id-480aar99:before,.ffb-id-480aar99:after,.ffb-id-480aar99 *,.ffb-id-480aar99 *:before,.ffb-id-480aar99 *:after{